{"tid":1907442,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"【精華整合】為大家總結下呢半年來嘅血與淚","createTime":"2020-03-02T15:10:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T09:02:29.000Z","uid":183576,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"539a82e4e7eecaeba0ae1be9b48e75e026480379","tid":1907442,"uid":183576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T15:10:21.000Z","msg":"反送中轉眼已經過去八個月，每個人都失去左好多野，但革命遠遠未成功，大家唔好鬆懈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟喺呢度幫大家整合左呢半年嘅精品反送中歌，希望可以喚返起各位手足奮戰嘅心<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLW6TDmDL5Z1iK3oi09QslknFXkdt83GFC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fplaylist%3Flist%3DPLW6TDmDL5Z1iK3oi09QslknFXkdt83GFC&d=FoM%2FNT%2BxDvRLDdkWKwCN%2BBZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=b5219880\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLW6TDmDL5Z1iK3oi09QslknFXkdt83GFC</a><br />\n<br />\n歌單順序<br />\n1. 願榮光歸香港<br />\n2. 不屈進行曲<br />\n3. 和你飛<br />\n4. 自游<br />\n5. 虛作無聲<br />\n6. 雞蛋與羔羊<br />\n7. 獨家村<br />\n8. 二零一九<br />\n9. 假使世界原來不像你預期<br />\n10. 天佑我們<br />\n11. 香港之歌<br />\n12. 由這一分鐘開始送比中央等判監/ 心淡<br />\n13. 淚痕/ 木紋<br />\n14. 勇士三罷/ 富士山下<br />\n15. 造夢/ 落花流水<br />\n16. 煲底相見/ 就算世界無童話<br />\n17. 黃大嗶/ 嗶嗶嗶<br />\n18. 肥媽有話兒/ Chandelier<br />\n19. Sing Hallelujah to the Lord<br />\n20. 致所有對逝者不敬的人<br />\n21. 家明<br />\n22. 呢首...係最令我心痛嘅歌 請大家聽曬佢 記住佢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽住歌鬥志振作就好諗下點樣繼續抗爭啦，唔好要烈士嘅血白流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35e726e80350195f89838af6364319ae3e221660","tid":1907442,"uid":183576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T15:34:14.000Z","msg":"輕推"},{"pid":